                        <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-3">How to Build a WhatsApp Chatbot</h2>
                        <p>Creating a WhatsApp chatbot with our API is straightforward. Follow these steps to get your first chatbot running in minutes:</p>

                        <div class="card mb-4">
                            <div class="card-body">
